Description: Improve SDL2 migration
 - cool_mzx: save SDL_TimerID and use SDL_RemoveTimer() to cancel the timer;
   SDL_AddTimer(0,NULL,NULL) was incorrect and is not the SDL2 equivalent
   of SDL1's SDL_SetTimer(0,NULL)
 - main: move SDL_SetHint before SDL_CreateRenderer so the hint takes effect
 - main: use SDL_RenderSetLogicalSize(640,480) for automatic aspect-ratio
   letterboxing instead of manual viewport management
 - main: remove resize_window() which contained dead SDL_RenderGetViewport
   code and is now superseded by SDL_RenderSetLogicalSize
 - main: remove window-event handler that accessed SDL_WindowEvent fields
   for all event types (undefined behaviour)
Author: Nicolas HOUDELOT <nicolas@demosdebs.org>
Applied-Upstream: no
Last-Update: 2026-04-21
